# Terraform state & working dirs
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Real variable values & secrets (never commit)
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
*.auto.tfvars
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# SSH keys, if placed here by mistake
*.pem
id_*
*.pub
